Maud Durbin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maud_Durbin 0 Maud Durbin (November 9, 1871 – December 25, 1936) was an American actress. She was the wife of actor Otis Skinner and the mother of actress and author Cornelia Otis Skinner. Maud_Durbin ( November_9_,_1871 – December_25_,_1936 ) was an_American_actress .
